    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A baby floor mat, also called a playmat, play gym, or an activity mat is a brightly colored, interactive mat for a baby or toddler. They come in a variety of sizes, shapes, and themes, but almost all have a few small toys, such as mirrors, rattles, jingles, or crinkle toys.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
